
DEUS, qui cónspicis quia ex nulla nostra virtúte subsístimus: concéde propítius; ut, intercessióne beáti Martíni Confessóris tui atque Pontíficis, contra ómnia advérsa muniámur. Per Dóminum.
O GOD, who seest that we stand not by any strength of our own; mercifully grant that, by the intercession of blessed Martin thy Confessor and Bishop, we may be defended against all adversity. Through our Lord.
